import "./App.css"; import { CurriculoService } from "./services/CurriculoService"; import {CepService} from "./services/CepService" import React from "react"; const dataInit = { cep: "", logradouro: "", bairro: "", cidade: "", uf: "" } class App extends React.Component { constructor(props){ super(props); this.state = { date: dataInit } } Enviar = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const formData = new FormData(e.target); const data = Object.fromEntries(formData); CurriculoService.apiPost(data); }; async buscarCep() { const cep = document.querySelector('.cep1').value + document.querySelector('.cep2').value; if(cep.lenght < 8){ return; } await CepService.ConsultaCep(cep).then(result => { if(result.hasOwnProperty("erro")){ alert('CEP não existente'); } else{ this.state.uf = result.uf; this.state.cidade = result.localidade; this.state.bairro = result.bairro; this.state.logradouro = result.logradouro; } }); }; handleChange = (e) => { const value = e.target.value; const name = e.target.name; this.setState({ [name]: value}, () => { this.buscarCep(); }); } render(){ return(














































































)}; } export default App;
